msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "FreeIntv is a libretro emulation core for the Mattel Intellivision designed for joypad compatibility."
msgstr "FreeIntv je emulační jádro Libretro pro Mattel Intellivision navržené pro kompatibilitu s gamepady."

